'''颶風菲利克斯'''是大西洋有紀錄以來，以五級颶風強度登陸地點最南的熱帶氣旋。它是[[2007年大西洋颶風季|當年風季]]第六個被命名的風暴與第二場颶風，同時是當年風季第二個五級颶風。菲利克斯起源於一股東風波，通過向风群岛後迅速發展到五級颶風強度，之後先暫時性失去五級颶風強度，9月4日重回五級颶風強度後，在[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]與[[宏都拉斯|宏都拉斯]]交界的大西洋沿岸附近[[登陸_(氣象學)|登陸]]，並造成133人罹難和數億美元的損失，遭到除名。

==氣象歷史==
{{storm path|Felix_2007_track.png}}
菲利克斯起源於在8月24日位於非洲西岸的[[东风波|东风波]]，以每小時23公里的速度向西移動，當時沒有較明顯的對流<ref name="Felix TCR">{{cite web|author=Jack Beven|title=Hurricane Felix Tropical Cyclone Report|date=2008-01-16|publisher=[[National_Hurricane_Center|National Hurricane Center]]|accessdate=2011-03-04|url={{NHC TCR url|id=AL062007_Felix}}}}</ref><ref name="824disc">{{cite web|author=Patricia Wallace|date=2007-08-24|title=August 24 Tropical Weather Discussion|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/Atl-Dis/2007082405.AXNT20}}{{dead link|date=November 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，令中心難以在[[氣象衛星雲圖|衛星雲圖]]上定位<ref name="824disc2">{{cite web|author=Patricia Wallace|date=2007-08-24|title=August 24 Tropical Weather Discussion (2)|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2007-09-01|url=ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/Atl-Dis/2007082417.AXNT20}}{{dead link|date=November 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，在潮濕溫暖的海洋環境中形成了零星的雷暴<ref name="825disc">{{cite web|author=John Cangialosi|date=2007-08-25|title=August 25 Tropical Weather Discussion|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/Atl-Dis/2007082505.AXNT20}}{{dead link|date=November 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，隔日可見光衛星雲圖可見熱帶擾動的逆時針轉動<ref name="825disc2">{{cite web|author=John Cangialosi|date=2007-08-25|title=August 25 Tropical Weather Discussion (2)|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/Atl-Dis/2007082510.AXNT20}}{{dead link|date=November 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，熱帶擾動位於[[熱帶輻合帶|熱帶輻合帶]]北側，適合熱帶氣旋發展，擾動向西移動的同時，對流的強度也增加<ref name="827disc">{{cite web|author=Mike Formosa|date=2007-08-27|title=August 27 Tropical Weather Discussion|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/Atl-Dis/2007082718.AXNT20}}{{dead link|date=November 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>；在經過幾天沒有重大發展後<ref name="830two">{{cite web|author=Michelle Mainelli|date=2007-08-30|title=August 30 Tropical Weather Outlook|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/Outlook-A/2007083009.ABNT20}}{{dead link|date=November 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，在8月30日開始進一步發展<ref name="830twd">{{cite web|author=Jorge Augierre-Echevarria|date=2007-08-30|title=August 30 Tropical Weather Discussion|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/Atl-Dis/2007083023.AXNT20}}{{dead link|date=November 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，隔日對流明顯增加，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]觀察出封閉的低層環流，國家颶風中心認定此系統增強為當年北大西洋第六個熱帶性低氣壓<ref name="831two">{{cite web|author=Richard Knabb|date=2007-08-31|title=August 31 Tropical Weather Outlook|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=ftp://ftp.met.fsu.edu/pub/weather/tropical/Outlook-A/2007083109.ABNT20}}{{dead link|date=November 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="disc1">{{cite web|author=Eric Blake & Lixion Avila|date=2007-08-31|title=Tropical Depression Six Discussion One|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.001.shtml?}}</ref>。

形成熱帶性低氣壓後，該熱帶性低氣壓位於強烈的副熱帶高氣壓南邊，導致熱帶性低氣壓繼續向西移動，同時偏低的[[风切变|垂直風切變]]及偏高的[[海面温度|海水溫度]]，導致熱帶性低氣壓持續增強<ref name="disc1"/>，在通過[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]不久後，增強為熱帶風暴，國家颶風中心命名為菲利克斯<ref name="disc3">{{cite web|author=Richard Knabb|date=2007-09-01|title=Tropical Storm Felix Discussion Three|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.003.shtml?}}</ref>，之後菲利克斯繼續增強，形成中心密集雲團<ref name="disc4">{{cite web|author=Eric Blake & Lixion Avila|date=2007-09-01|title=Tropical Storm Felix Discussion Four|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.004.shtml?}}</ref>，並逐漸打開風眼<ref name="disc5">{{cite web|author=Eric Blake & Lixion Avila|date=2007-09-01|title=Tropical Storm Felix Discussion Five|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.005.shtml?}}</ref>，透過颶風獵人觀測，菲利克斯在9月2日上午增強到颶風強度<ref name="pa5a">{{cite web|author=Jack Beven|date=2007-09-01|title=Hurricane Felix Intermediate Public Advisory Five-A|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public_a.005.shtml?}}</ref>。

[[Image:Felix_2007-09-02_1748Z.jpg|thumb]]
在增強為颶風後，菲利克斯從海洋熱含量中吸收能量，使其[[快速增强|快速增强]]並形成清晰可見的[[風眼|風眼]]，當日便增強為[[SSHS#分級|大型颶風]]<ref name="disc8">{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-02|title=Hurricane Felix Discussion Eight|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.008.shtml?}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-02|title=Hurricane Felix Intermediate Public Advisory Eight-A|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public_a.008.shtml?}}</ref>，增強為大型颶風後仍繼續快速增強，呈現體育場效應<ref name="disc9">{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-02|title=Hurricane Felix Discussion Nine|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.009.shtml?}}</ref>經過颶風獵人的觀察，菲利克斯中心附近最大的一分鐘平均風速為145節，達到五級颶風強度，此時颶風中心位於[[牙买加|牙买加]][[京斯敦|京斯敦]]東南方625公里<ref name="disc10">{{cite web|author=James Franklin & Daniel Brown|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Special Discussion Ten|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.010.shtml?}}</ref>。

之後向西移動，菲利克斯的風眼直徑僅19公里<ref name="disc12"/>，在成為五級颶風後七小時仍繼續增強至巔峰，最大一分鐘平均風速為150節，中心氣壓929[[帕斯卡|百帕]]<ref name="Felix TCR"/>，最初，國家颶風中心一度預測菲利克斯會進入墨西哥灣<ref name="disc12">{{cite web|author=Richard Knabb|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Discussion Twelve|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.012.shtml?}}</ref>然而，颶風移動的路徑較原先預期偏南，隨後進入[[眼牆置換週期|眼牆置換週期]]<ref name="disc13">{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Discussion Thirteen|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.013.shtml?}}</ref>，在此期間颶風一度失去五級颶風強度<ref name="pa13a">{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Intermediate Public Advisory Thirteen-A|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public_a.013.shtml?}}</ref>；在9月4日菲利克斯完成眼牆置換週期，重返五級颶風強度<ref>{{cite web|author=Richard Knabb|date=2007-09-04|title=Hurricane Felix Discussion Sixteen|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.016.shtml?}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Richard Knabb|date=2007-09-04|title=Hurricane Felix Tropical Cyclone Update|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.update.09041040.shtml?}}</ref>，不過不久後颶風從宏都拉斯和尼加拉瓜附近的海岸進入陸地<ref>{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-04|title=Hurricane Felix Public Advisory Sixteen-A|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public_a.016.shtml?}}</ref>，在陸地上受到地形影響，強度迅速減弱，很快便失去大型颶風強度<ref>{{cite web|author=National Climatic Data Center|accessdate=2008-03-16|year=2007|title=September 2007 Global Hazards and Significant Events|url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2007/sep/hazards.html}}</ref><ref name="disc18">{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-04|title=Hurricane Felix Discussion Eighteen|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.018.shtml?}}</ref>，隔日上午便減弱為熱帶風暴<ref name="disc19">{{cite web|author=Jack Beven|date=2007-09-05|title=Tropical Storm Felix Discussion Nineteen|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.019.shtml?}}</ref>，由於地形複雜，菲利克斯在當日便減弱為[[後熱帶氣旋|殘餘低壓]]，國家颶風中心發出最後一報<ref name="disc20">{{cite web|author=Lixion Avila|date=2007-09-05|title=Tropical Depression Felix Discussion Twenty|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.discus.020.shtml?}}</ref>，隨後殘餘低壓進入墨西哥境內消散<ref name="Felix TCR"/>。

==防災措施==
[[Image:Felix_3_sept_2007_1830Z.jpg|thumb]]
在菲利克斯成為熱帶氣旋後，熱帶風暴警告在[[圣文森特和格林纳丁斯|圣文森特和格林纳丁斯]]、[[多巴哥岛|多巴哥]]和[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]生效<ref name="pa1">{{cite web|author=Eric Blake & Lixion Avila|date=2007-08-31|title=Tropical Depression Six Public Advisory One|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public.001.shtml?}}</ref>多巴哥國家緊急事務管理局啟動的79個避難所<ref name="trin91">{{cite web|author=Driselle Ramjohn |year=2007 |title=Storm Lashes Tobago |publisher=Trinidad & Tobago Express |url=http://www.trinidadexpress.com/index.pl/article_news?id=161197326 <!--|url-status=dead -->|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071104142510/http://www.trinidadexpress.com/index.pl/article_news?id=161197326 |archivedate=2007-11-04 }}</ref>，隨者熱帶性低氣壓增強為熱帶風暴，熱帶風暴警告也在[[ABC群島|ABC群島]]生效<ref name="pa3">{{cite web|author=Richard Knabb|date=2007-09-03|title=Tropical Storm Felix Public Advisory Three|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public.003.shtml?}}</ref>，同時颶風觀察預警也在這些島嶼生效，島上有些遊客趕在颶風來臨前搭飛機離開，<ref name="pa6">{{cite web|author=Jack Beven|date=2007-09-02|title=Hurricane Felix Public Advisory Six|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public.006.shtml}}</ref>，熱帶風暴觀察預警一度在牙買加生效<ref name="pa5a"/>，不過路徑偏南，熱帶風暴警告沒在當地生效<ref name="pa13a"/>，到了9月2日熱帶風暴觀察預警在[[大開曼|大開曼]]生效<ref name="pa8">{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-02|title=Hurricane Felix Public Advisory Eight|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public.008.shtml}}</ref>，隔天熱帶風暴警告在[[普羅維登西亞島|普羅維登西亞島]]生效<ref>{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Public Advisory Fourteen|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public.014.shtml?}}</ref>；9月3日颶風觀察預警開始在[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]生效<ref name="pa12a">{{cite web|author=Richard Pasch|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Intermediate Public Advisory Twelve-A|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public_a.012.shtml?}}</ref>

在世界標準時間9月3日上午3時，颶風觀察預警在利蒙到洪都拉斯與尼加拉瓜的交界生效<ref name="pa11">{{cite web|author=James Franklin|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Public Advisory Eleven|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public.011.shtml}}</ref>，在六小時後颶風警告在該地生效。同時，颶風觀察預警向西延伸至洪都拉斯與危地馬拉的邊界<ref name="pa12">{{cite web|author=Richard Knabb|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Public Advisory Twelve|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public.012.shtml}}</ref>，到了隔天熱帶風暴警告在該地區生效<ref name="pa15">{{cite web|author=James Franklin|date=2007-09-04|title=Hurricane Felix Public Advisory Fifteen|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public.015.shtml}}</ref>，當地政府協助在靠近海岸線的低窪地區居民撤離<ref name="ap93">{{cite web|author=Associated Press|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Aims for Central America|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.cfnews13.com/News/International/2007/9/3/hurricane_felix_aims_for_central_america.html |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927194521/http://www.cfnews13.com/News/International/2007/9/3/hurricane_felix_aims_for_central_america.html |archivedate = 2007-09-27}}</ref>，大約有2000人從沿海地區撤離<ref name="ap93a">{{cite web|author=Associated Press|date=2007-09-03|title=Tourists flee as Hurricane Felix nears Honduran Miskito Coast|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.pr-inside.com/tourists-flee-as-hurricane-felix-nears-r218680.htm| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070926220125/http://www.pr-inside.com/tourists-flee-as-hurricane-felix-nears-r218680.htm| archivedate = September 26, 2007}}</ref>，在颶風登陸時，宏都拉斯約有，宏都拉斯約有2萬人撤離到更安全的地區<ref name="afp96">{{cite web|author=Agence French-Presse |date=2007-09-06 |title=Drenched by Felix, Honduras fears floods, mudslides |accessdate=2011-03-04 |url=http://www.citizen.co.za/index/Article.aspx?pDesc=1,1,22&Type=top&File=070905174206.0tvihxpa.xml <!--|url-status=dead -->|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080609042239/http://www.citizen.co.za/index/Article.aspx?pDesc=1%2C1%2C22&Type=top&File=070905174206.0tvihxpa.xml |archivedate=2008-06-09 }}</ref>。

在世界協調時間9月3日下午3時，颶風警告在[[卡貝薩斯港|卡貝薩斯港]]以北到尼加拉瓜邊境沿海生效<ref name="pa13">{{cite web|author=Richard Knabb|date=2007-09-03|title=Hurricane Felix Public Advisory Thirteen|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public.013.shtml}}</ref>，之後熱帶風暴警告從該港口到[[普林薩波卡|普林薩波卡]]間沿海生效<ref name="pa15"/>，在颶風來臨之前，當地政府準備了14萬[[磅|磅]]的應急物資<ref name="ap95">{{cite web|author=Associated Press|date=2007-09-05|title=Toll from Felix rises in Central America; Henriette nears 2nd Mexican landfall|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://canadianpress.google.com/article/ALeqM5iSudi_zF2sSIwQCZxmeLL990M_Dw}}{{dead link|date=November 2012|bot=Legobot}}</ref>。

==影響==
===加勒比海群島===
[[Image:Aruba-Hurricane-Felix-1.jpg|left]]
在世界協調時間9月1日，[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]的測站測得每小時74公里的陣風，同時[[圣文森特岛|圣文森特岛]]測得每小時71公里的陣風<ref name="pa3a">{{cite web|author=Eric Blake & Lixion Avila|date=2007-09-01|title=Tropical Storm Felix Intermediate Public Advisory Three-A|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al06/al062007.public_a.003.shtml?}}</ref>；風暴造成大雨，在[[特立尼达岛|特立尼达岛]]造成[[泥石流|泥石流]]與洪水氾濫，有些橋梁遭到沖毀，大風也導致數棟建築物受損；風暴對[[多巴哥岛|多巴哥岛]]的破壞集中在該島北部，有幾處山坡地發生了土石流<ref name="cbc91">{{cite web|author=Caribbean Broadcasting Corporation|date=2007-09-01|title=TS Felix brings rain and damage|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.cbc.bb/content/view/12414/45/|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927001345/http://www.cbc.bb/content/view/12414/45/|archivedate = 2007-09-27}}</ref>，經濟損失估計為25萬[[特立尼达和多巴哥元|特立尼达和多巴哥元]]<ref>{{cite web|author=Jensen LaVende|date=2007-09-02|title=Cars, shop swept away at Carenage|publisher=Trinidad & Tobago Express|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.trinidadexpress.com/index.pl/article_news?id=161197574| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070903230004/http://www.trinidadexpress.com/index.pl/article_news?id=161197574| archivedate = September 3, 2007}}</ref>，在[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]，菲利克斯摧毀了多條電線以及兩棟房屋的屋頂，引發的大浪摧毀在海上拋錨的船<ref name="ap91">{{cite web|author=Associated Press|date=2007-09-01|title=Felix becomes Category 1 hurricane as it swirls toward Aruba|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://canadianpress.google.com/article/ALeqM5jqMWKNh_ilvCvWappNmBJfwMGWFg}}{{dead link|date=September 2016|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>；在[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]，一家商店的屋頂被吹掀，吹掀的屋頂破壞十二輛汽車<ref name="cbc91"/>。

在[[ABC群島|ABC群島]]，颶風導致大風大雨，在[[博奈尔|博奈尔]]的破壞較少，在[[库拉索|库拉索]]造成了淹水，在[[阿魯巴|阿魯巴]]有一棟房屋被摧毀，該島北部發生停電情況<ref name="ap93x">{{cite web|author=Associated Press|year=2007|title=Hurricane Felix lashes Dutch Caribbean islands|accessdate=|url=}}</ref><!--{{fcn|date=December 2017}}-->，此外颶風在委內瑞拉產生三公尺的巨浪，該國的[[卡貝略港|卡貝略港]]有一人因此失蹤<ref name="afp93">{{cite web|author=Agence French-Presse |date=2007-09-03 |title=Furious Hurricane Felix heads for landfall |accessdate=2007-09-03 |url=http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5jqK-v2ow8GjpYjB3tHUvxe5-pNbw <!--|url-status=dead -->|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090707142638/http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5jqK-v2ow8GjpYjB3tHUvxe5-pNbw |archivedate=2009-07-07 }}</ref>。

===中美洲===
[[Image:Felix_04_sept_2007_1610Z.jpg|thumb]]
菲利克斯以五級颶風強度登陸後，在宏都拉斯與尼加拉瓜造成嚴重破壞，卡貝薩斯港的屋頂幾乎全部被吹掀；在[[蚊子海岸|蚊子海岸]]，菲利克斯所帶來的洪水和土石流摧毀的許多房屋，也造成高速公路的中斷<ref name="latimes1">{{cite web|author=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|url = http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-storms6sep06,1,1334146.story?track=rss |title = Tropical Storm Abates in Tabasco — |accessdate = 2008-07-18 }}{{dead link|date=September 2016|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>，在卡貝薩斯港是災情最嚴重的地方，米斯基托珊瑚礁幾乎全部被摧毀<ref>{{cite web|title=Hurricane Felix and the Miskito Cays |year=2007 |publisher=ViaNica |url=http://www.vianica.com/projects/1/ |accessdate=2011-03-04 <!--|url-status=dead -->|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110323135111/http://vianica.com/projects/1/ |archivedate=2011-03-23 }}</ref>。

根據新聞報導，133名罹難人士中，有130人在尼加拉瓜<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mobile.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/N07466455.htm|year=2007|title=Hurricane Felix death toll hits 130 for Nicaragua|author=Reuters|accessdate=2008-07-18}}</ref><ref name="latimes1"/>，其餘3人在宏都拉斯<ref name="physorg1">{{cite web|url=http://www.physorg.com/news108395306.html|author=Physorg.com|date=2007-09-07|accessdate=2011-02-28|title=Search goes on for Hurricane Felix victims|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929121824/http://www.physorg.com/news108395306.html|archivedate=2007-09-29}}</ref>，但這些數據不包含失蹤者，估計在海上有數百名失蹤者，其中僅有少數失蹤者被沖到蚊子海岸倖存<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1Y1-110112020.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105171032/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1Y1-110112020.html<!--|url-status=dead-->|archive-date=2012-11-05|agency=Associated Press|publisher=HighBeam Research|date=2007-09-06|accessdate=2011-03-04|title=Felix Death Toll Rises to 64}}</ref>；根據官方資料，至少有40,000人受災，並摧毀了9,000所房屋，其中大多數在尼加拉瓜[[卡貝薩斯港|卡貝薩斯港]]，政府也發出了災難狀態，當地幾乎完全與外界隔絕；災難發生後的第二天，當地總統到卡貝薩斯港勘災<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvnz.co.nz/view/page/1318360/1335477 |author=Rueters |publisher=[[Television_New_Zealand|Television New Zealand]] |date=2007-09-06 |accessdate=2011-03-04 |title=Felix devastates Nicaragua <!--|url-status=dead -->|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516062400/http://tvnz.co.nz/view/page/1318360/1335477 |archivedate=2011-05-16 }}</ref>，該國的經濟損失達到134億[[尼加拉瓜科多巴|尼加拉瓜科多巴]]<ref>{{cite web|author=Organización de las Naciones Unidas para la Agricultura y la Alimentación (FAO), Nicaragua|year=2007|title=Evaluación de Daños Causados por el Huracán Félix en el Caribe de Nicaragua.|accessdate=2008-03-24|format=PDF|url=http://www.fao.org/fileadmin/templates/tc/tce/pdf/Nicaragua_FAO_Evaluacion_2007.pdf|language=es|archive-date=2012-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017092251/http://www.fao.org/fileadmin/templates/tc/tce/pdf/Nicaragua_FAO_Evaluacion_2007.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=José Adán Silva |publisher=El Nuevo Diario |date=January 29, 2008 |accessdate=April 14, 2010 |title=Huracán los terminó de hundir en la pobreza |url=http://impreso.elnuevodiario.com.ni/2007/01/29/especiales/84368 |language=es <!--|url-status=dead -->|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122094329/http://impreso.elnuevodiario.com.ni/2007/01/29/especiales/84368 |archivedate=January 22, 2009 }}</ref>。

在宏都拉斯亦出現洪水，兩條河流氾濫造成農田被淹<ref name="physorg1"/>，農業損失達到68.28億[[宏都拉斯倫皮拉|宏都拉斯倫皮拉]]<ref>{{cite web|author=[[Comisión_Permanente_de_Contingencias|COPECO]], Government of Honduras|date=2007-09-07|title=Honduras: Informe preliminar de daños por Huracán Félix y últimas lluvias — Copeco — Boletín #53 - 07 de Septiembre 2007|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.reliefweb.int/rw/rwb.nsf/db900sid/LRON-76YCLW?OpenDocument|language=es|archive-date=2008-02-17|archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20080217164212/http://www.reliefweb.int/rw/rwb.nsf/db900sid/LRON-76YCLW?OpenDocument|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==善後及後續==
由於菲利克斯造成嚴重的經濟損失，[[联合国|联合国]]提供了4800萬美元的救助給受災地區<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2007/09/15/2033842.htm|title=UN calls on world to help Nicaragua rebuild|accessdate=2011-03-04|date=2007-09-15|publisher=ABC News}}</ref>，而美利堅合眾國聯邦政府提供了117萬美元的援助<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.redorbit.com/news/health/1063022/usaid_hurricane_assistance_to_nicaragua_increases/index.html|title=USAID Hurricane Assistance to Nicaragua Increases|accessdate=2011-03-04|date=2007-09-11|publisher=RedOrbit}}</ref>，[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]也提供了100萬[[欧元|欧元]]的援助<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.rian.ru/world/20070907/77356234.html|title=EU to donate 1 million euros to help post-Felix Nicaragua|accessdate=2011-03-04|date=2007-09-07|publisher=RIA Novosti}}</ref>，除金錢援助外，也有物資援助送往受災地區<ref name="factsheet #8 ">{{cite web|url=http://www.reliefweb.int/rw/RWB.NSF/db900SID/YSAR-779U49?OpenDocument&rc=2&emid=TC-2007-000150-BLZ|title=Latin America and the Caribbean – Hurricane Season 2007 Fact Sheet #8 (FY 2007)|author=[[United_States_Agency_for_International_Development|United States Agency for International Development]]|year=2007|publisher=ReliefWeb |accessdate=2011-03-07}}</ref>；另外，由於菲利克斯在尼加拉瓜造成廣泛的破壞，菲利克斯在2008年5月13日遭到世界氣象組織除名，由[[熱帶風暴費爾南德|費爾南德]]取代<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.noaanews.noaa.gov/stories2008/20080513_stormnames.html|title=Dean, Felix and Noel "Retired" from List of Storm Names|accessdate=2011-03-04|date=2008-05-13|publisher=[[National_Oceanic_and_Atmospheric_Administration|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]]|archive-date=2013-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130807135700/http://www.noaanews.noaa.gov/stories2008/20080513_stormnames.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

